a) For adding a new timer, use primary action buttons - https://designguidelines.withgoogle.com/wearos/components/primary-action-buttons.html

b) Swipe right-to-left on items in the list to reveal edit/delete action.

c) When a timer goes off, launch the app on the timer screen.

d) Allow hardware buttons on the watch to silence the timer when it goes off.

*f) I want to use Kotlin to build this app.
*g) 50% code coverage with JUnit is preferable.